snippet.textDisplay:
I am a huge fan of korean dramas..
Before, i didn't know about bts.. on friday, around 2pm i saw black swan trending in Twitter (Pakistan)..
I thought what could it be that korean music is trending here.. out of curiosity I searched black swan on YouTube and it was released few hours ago..
All comments were saying bts Army... I was so surprised.. i didn't saw such huge fanfollowing of any idol group...
As they are koreans,so it is really difficult to recognize them because they all look same..we hardly differentiate between chinese, korean, Japanese..they all look same.. i used to think how mothers recognize thrir child(before watching korean dramas)..in k dramas i recognize their features after 8 episode.. no offence🙂....it took me about 15 hours to recognize them because jungkook and jin totally look like twins..

After watching so many videos and interview etc , i was able to recognize their features..
And i learned their names..
Its

RM
V
J-hope
Suga
Jin
Jimin
Jeon jungkook...

What i like most is their friendship.. for some reason the group friendship always attract me.. and they have incredible coordination..
After that I ended up watching all their music videos, run bts episodes, fan made videos within week..

And still wondering that i m watching all korean music..

Their music and dance is deep, mysterious.. and also they themselves look so deep, unique and special...the interaction between members is so strong and beautiful.. love their bond..

Am i included in this army?
Still thinking
Am i their fan?

Because its hardly one month , i started watching them...




Pakistan zindabad 🇵🇰
